{#
  Monograph Template
  ==================
  Comprehensive scholarly treatment: Context, Canon, Method, Analysis.
  For in-depth academic treatment of a subject.

  Required Variables:
  - title: Paper title
  - author: Author name(s)
  - abstract: Paper abstract

  Optional Variables:
  - context: Contextual background content
  - canon: Canonical literature review content
  - method: Methodological approach content
  - analysis: Analysis and interpretation content
  - date: Publication date (defaults to \today)
  - bibliography: Bibliography file name (defaults to 'references')

  Usage:
    const context = {
      title: "A Comprehensive Study of X",
      author: "Scholarly Author",
      abstract: "This monograph provides...",
      context: "Historical development of...",
      canon: "Key works in the field include...",
      method: "Our approach combines...",
      analysis: "Deep analysis reveals..."
    };
#}
\documentclass{article}
\usepackage{hyperref}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{graphicx}

\title{{ '{' }}{{ title | texescape }}{{ '}' }}
\author{{ '{' }}{{ author | texescape }}{{ '}' }}
\date{{ '{' }}{% if date %}{{ date | texescape }}{% else %}\today{% endif %}{{ '}' }}

\begin{document}
\maketitle

\begin{abstract}
{{ abstract | texescape }}
\end{abstract}

% Monograph Thesis Structure: Context, Canon, Method, Analysis
% This structure provides comprehensive scholarly treatment of a subject

\section{Context}
{% if context %}{{ context | texescape }}{% endif %}

Comprehensive contextual background establishing the research setting, historical development, and contemporary relevance of the subject matter.

\section{Canon}
{% if canon %}{{ canon | texescape }}{% endif %}

Review of the canonical literature and established scholarship, positioning this work within the broader academic discourse.

\section{Method}
{% if method %}{{ method | texescape }}{% endif %}

Detailed methodological approach employed in this research, including theoretical frameworks, data collection, and analytical procedures.

\section{Analysis}
{% if analysis %}{{ analysis | texescape }}{% endif %}

In-depth analysis and interpretation of findings, synthesizing evidence and constructing scholarly arguments based on the investigation.

